{"id": "hard_la_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Linear Algebra", "question": "求所有满足 A² = I 的 2×2 实矩阵 A（对合矩阵）。", "answer": "设A = [[a, b], [c, d]]，则A² = [[a²+bc, b(a+d)], [c(a+d), d²+bc]] = I\n条件1: a²+bc = 1, d²+bc = 1, b(a+d)=0, c(a+d)=0\n\n分两类情况:\n情况I: a+d ≠ 0 → b=0, c=0 → a²=1, d²=1 → a=±1, d=±1\nA = [[±1, 0], [0, ±1]]\n\n情况II: a+d = 0 → d = -a, 且 a²+bc = 1\nA = [[a, b], [c, -a]]，其中 a²+bc=1\n\n所以对合矩阵通解为: [[a, b], [c, -a]] (a²+bc=1) 和单位矩阵的变号 [[1,0],[0,1]], [[-1,0],[0,-1]]"}
{"id": "hard_geo_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Geometry", "question": "四面体ABCD中AB=CD=5, AC=BD=6, AD=BC=7，求体积。", "answer": "已知四面体ABCD，AB=CD=5, AC=BD=6, AD=BC=7\n这是三组对边相等的四面体（等腰四面体）\n\n用体积公式: V = √[ (a²+b²-c²)(b²+c²-a²)(c²+a²-b²) ] / (6√2)\n其中 a=AB=5, b=AC=6, c=AD=7\n\na²=25, b²=36, c²=49\n(a²+b²-c²) = 25+36-49 = 12\n(b²+c²-a²) = 36+49-25 = 60\n(c²+a²-b²) = 49+25-36 = 38\n\nV = √(12×60×38) / (6√2) = √(27360) / (6√2) = √27360 / (6√2) = √(27360/2) / 6 = √13680 / 6\n\n用execute_code验证"}
{"id": "hard_analysis_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Mathematical Analysis", "question": "计算极限：lim_{x→0} (e^x - 1 - x - x²/2) / x³", "answer": "lim_{x→0} (e^x - 1 - x - x²/2) / x³\n\n用泰勒展开: e^x = 1 + x + x²/2 + x³/6 + x⁴/24 + ...\n\ne^x - 1 - x - x²/2 = x³/6 + x⁴/24 + ...\n\n所以极限 = lim_{x→0} (x³/6 + x⁴/24 + ...) / x³ = lim_{x→0} (1/6 + x/24 + ...) = 1/6\n\n答案: 1/6"}
{"id": "hard_nt_3", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Number Theory", "question": "求 2024! 末尾有多少个连续的零？", "answer": "末尾零的个数 = 因子5的个数（因为2的个数总是多于5）\n\n⌊2024/5⌋ = 404\n⌊2024/25⌋ = 80\n⌊2024/125⌋ = 16\n⌊2024/625⌋ = 3\n\n总数 = 404 + 80 + 16 + 3 = 503\n\n答案: 503个连续的零"}
{"id": "hard_calc_2", "source": "high_difficulty_math", "difficulty": "expert", "type": "Calculus", "question": "求函数 f(x)=x⁴-4x³+6x²-4x+1 的极值点和拐点。f(x)=(x-1)⁴ 是否有帮助？", "answer": "f(x) = x⁴ - 4x³ + 6x² - 4x + 1 = (x-1)⁴\n\nf'(x) = 4(x-1)³ = 0 → x = 1\nf''(x) = 12(x-1)²\nf''(1) = 0, 但f'''(x)=24(x-1), f'''(1)=0, f⁽⁴⁾(1)=24>0\n\nx=1是极小值点（也是拐点？f''(x)=0说明在检查）\n实际(x-1)⁴的图形：x=1处取得最小值0，是全局极小值点\nf''(x)=12(x-1)² ≥ 0，没有拐点（二阶导不变号）\n\n极值点：x=1处全局极小值f(1)=0\n拐点：无（f''(x)恒≥0，函数下凸）"}
